  "top_positive_factors": ["morning commuter flow", "gym adjacency"],
  "top_risks": ["rent pressure", "ingress friction"]
}

POST /v1/markets/search

Searches a metro for best candidate cells/sites.

POST /v1/simulate

Runs scenario analysis.

POST /v1/analogs

Finds similar sites, neighborhoods, or store archetypes.

POST /v1/explain

Returns explanation card for a score.

POST /v1/operator/upload

Uploads existing locations and performance history.

