13. Evaluation

You need three kinds of eval.

A. Ranking eval

Does it put good sites above bad ones?

Metrics:
	•	NDCG
	•	MAP
	•	top-k hit rate

B. Calibration eval

Are score and confidence honest?

Metrics:
	•	calibration error
	•	prediction interval coverage

C. Business eval

Would following the model have improved outcomes?

Metrics:
	•	backtested uplift
	•	avoided bad-site rate
	•	white-space discovery rate

