14. Threat model / failure controls

Risks
	•	stale data
	•	leakage from future info
	•	overconfidence from weak comps
	•	semantic hallucination
	•	misuse for discriminatory site selection

Controls
	•	versioned feature snapshots
	•	strict as-of dating
	•	uncertainty floor
	•	source lineage
	•	model cards
	•	policy filters on sensitive use

Important distinction:
This tool should optimize place performance, not proxy personal protected attributes.

